{"tid":2261000,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"【又係馬】奧巴馬：獨裁者希望特朗普贏  因特朗普會畀着數","createTime":"2020-10-28T04:20:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T01:49:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":339,"uniUserReply":118,"replies":[{"pid":"4b00ce5dfb7057b7431b4a8193b399b1769e00ee","tid":2261000,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:20:29.000Z","msg":"美國大選下周二（11月3日）舉行，前總統奧巴馬繼續四出為民主黨總統候選人拜登拉票。奧巴馬攻擊特朗普，指獨裁的國家領袖都希望總統特朗普連任，因特朗普會誘使獨裁者，並給他們一切所需的東西，但拜登不會妥協。<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬到佛州奧蘭多（Orlando）為拜登拉票時，談到特朗普與多名「獨裁者」（dictators）的關係。他表示，特朗普接受《60分鐘時事雜誌》（60 Minutes）訪問後，覺得主持「太過分」，並反問：<br />\n<br />\n「你認為他會站出來反對獨裁者？他認為主持斯塔爾（Lesley Stahl）是個惡霸。就在昨天，他說俄羅斯的普京、中國的習近平和北韓的金正恩希望他勝出。」（You think he's going to stand up to dictators? He thinks Lesley Stahl&rsquo;s a bully. Just yesterday, he said Putin of Russia, Xi of China, and Kim Jong Un of North Korea want him to win.）<br />\n<br />\n奧巴馬續稱：<br />\n<br />\n「我們知道，在過去4年，你（特朗普）一直在給他們想要的東西。當然，他們希望你贏。那不是好事。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2785000/2787813/2020102_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2785000%2F2787813%2F2020102_600.png&h=b4240a16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2787813</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3baef8b000469a2f4ad774a938cb36782dd75c23","tid":2261000,"uid":21545,"like":210,"dislike":2,"score":208,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:21:23.000Z","msg":"美國馬英九<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0c6951ed2f87f6d832f8ecd7996a7d23e98aeea","tid":2261000,"uid":121146,"like":83,"dislike":2,"score":81,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:21:33.000Z","msg":"下? 普京撐拜燈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d506f573e50f16f2a49f2552c3c3771948f2e6b3","tid":2261000,"uid":256943,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T04:21:40.000Z","msg":"下